    playNote(note, beats=4)

# create thicknes to the bass clef 
rest(8)

def play_chord(chord):
    playNote(chord, beats= 4)
    
# define a list of chords
chord_list = [[41, 45, 48], #FMaj
              [43, 47, 50],  # GMaj
              [45, 48, 52],  # Amin
              [50, 53, 57],  # Dmin
              [50, 53, 57],  # Dmin
              [45, 48, 52],  #Amin
              [43, 47, 50],  # GMaj
              [41, 45, 48], #FMaj
              [41, 45, 48], #FMaj
              [43, 47, 50],  # GMaj
              [45, 48, 52],  # Amin
              [50, 53, 57],  # Dmin
              [50, 53, 57],  # Dmin
              [45, 48, 52],  #Amin
              [43, 47, 50],  # GMaj
              [41, 45, 48]] #FMaj


# Map the function play_chord to each chord in the list
map(play_chord, chord_list)
